OL,3,CCharity says NI rise partly to blame
OL,4,Cas hospice staff laid off
OL,6,FA hospice charity said the rise in
OL,7,Femployers' National Insurance
OL,8,Fcontributions was partly to blame
OL,9,Fafter it laid off 19 workers.
OL,11,FHuddersfield-based The Kirkwood, which
OL,12,Fruns Kirkwood Hospice, said it needed
OL,13,Fto make redundancies to stay afloat.
OL,15,FAnother nine staff members have
OL,16,Freduced their hours and several others
OL,17,Fdecided to retire following a
OL,18,Fconsultation.
