OL,3,CCharity says NI rise partly to blame
OL,4,Cas hospice staff laid off
OL,6,FIn a statement, The Kirkwood said
OL,7,Fwages for its 250-strong workforce
OL,8,Fmade up the majority of its #11
OL,9,Fmillion annual budget.
OL,11,FIt said it was already facing a
OL,12,F"perfect storm" of growing demand and
OL,13,Fincreasing costs before it was
OL,14,Fannounced that National Insurance
OL,15,FContributions (NICs) would rise from
OL,16,Ffrom 13.8% to 15% last month.
