OL,3,CCharity says NI rise partly to blame
OL,4,Cas hospice staff laid off
OL,6,FIt said: "April's rise in the National
OL,7,FLiving Wage and National Insurance
OL,8,Fcontributions for employers further
OL,9,Fdeepened these financial pressures,
OL,10,Fleading to an announcement in January
OL,11,Fthat The Kirkwood needed to save #1.7m
OL,12,Feach year to put its finances back on
OL,13,Fa secure footing."
OL,15,FThe Kirkwood, which cares for people
OL,16,Fwith life-limiting illness like
OL,17,Fcancer, heart failure and motor
OL,18,Fneurone disease, provides palliative
OL,19,Fsupport at home and in care homes
OL,20,Facross Kirklees as well as at its own
OL,21,Fhospice.
