OL,3,CCharity says NI rise partly to blame
OL,4,Cas hospice staff laid off
OL,6,FIt receives only 25% of its funding
OL,7,Ffrom the NHS. The rest comes from
OL,8,Fdonations.
OL,10,FBosses say they have lost about #4m in
OL,11,Fthe last three years.
OL,13,FAs part of cost-cutting measures, the
OL,14,Fcharity will reduce the number of
OL,15,Finpatient beds from 16 to 12.
OL,17,FThe number of patients cared for by
OL,18,Fthe hospice will fall from about 2,100
OL,19,Fto 1,300.
