OL,4,Cas hospice staff laid off
OL,6,FChief executive Michael Crowther said:
OL,7,F"As you can imagine, this has been one
OL,8,Fof the most difficult periods in The
OL,9,FKirkwood's history.
OL,11,F"Having to make any of our highly
OL,12,Fskilled colleagues redundant is not
OL,13,Fsomething we ever thought we would
OL,14,Fhave to do.
