OL,3,CCharity says NI rise partly to blame
OL,4,Cas hospice staff laid off
OL,6,F"Our employees go above and beyond
OL,7,Fevery single day to provide the very
OL,8,Fbest care for our patients and
OL,9,Ffamilies and this has been the single
OL,10,Fhardest decision we have ever had to
OL,11,Fmake, but quite simply, we have to
OL,12,Fmake it now to ensure the long-term
OL,13,Ffuture of The Kirkwood."
OL,15,FThe government has said the rise in
OL,16,FNICs was necessary to fund public
OL,17,Fservices.
